text: Thank you so much for everything.

I'm glad
I got to work with you too!

Arisugawa-san, if we have the chance again,
please take care of me!

The staff seemed really grateful to Natsuha,
didn't they?

I think Natsuha's dedication to her work
contributed to the results this time.

But...
there's one thing I want you to remember.

It's because you're here that I can dedicate myself
to my work, so please don't forget that.
